## How to create a blog

First, we create the Next.js project with the following command:

```sh title="Terminal"
yarn create next-app nextjs-mdx-blog
```

Next, create the following file:

- `components\Layout.js` - Wrap all components in a container (optional, just the style)
- `date\blog\*.mdx` - Blog Articles
- `lib\formatDate.js` - Format the date as `MM DD, YYYY`
- `[slug].js` - article page, using [dynamic routes](https://nextjs.org/docs/routing/dynamic-routes)

